    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Given the company name and domain extracted from an employee email, provide a short description.\nCompany Name : {{ $('Set Details After Apollo Enrichment').item.json.company_name }}\nCompany Domain : {{ $('Set Details After Apollo Enrichment').item.json.attendee_company_domain }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are an AI business information lookup assistant. \nYour task is to provide a concise, accurate company description based on the given company domain. \nUse trusted business directories, company websites, and credible sources for the information. \nThe company description should summarize the company's industry, products or services, target market, and any notable facts, in 100 words. \nIf no reliable data is found, return \"not found\" for both fields. "
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        3312,
        624
      ],
      "id": "163d09f3-657b-47ac-a269-2fb03a2d6187",
      "name": "Company Description AI Agent",
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Use the context below to generate a concise, action‑ready pre‑call brief for Cobi, following the exact Output Structure and focusing on strategic value over repetition.​\n\nInputs:​\n\nCompany Details : \nCompany Description : ​{{ $json.company_description }}\n\nMeeting attendees and their roles: \nAttendee Name : ​{{ $json.attendee_full_name }}\nAttendee Title : {{ $json.attendee_title }}\n\nSalesforce Interaction Summary (Previous conversations, notes, or emails) : \n{{ $json.salesforce_interaction_summary }}\n\nMeeting Title: {{ $json.metting_title }}\nMeeting Description : {{ $json.meeting_description }}\n\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are a senior growth strategist and sales coach for Shout About Us — an API/platform that provides review data, responses, and insights for SaaS, data & analytics providers, and agencies.\n\nReference the other inputs such as:\nCompany background (industry, size, product, positioning, use case)\n\nMeeting attendees and their roles\n\nAny previous conversations, notes, or emails with this company provided through salesforce interaction summary.\n\nIf Salesforce Interaction summary Exists, ensure to use it for analysis and answering.\n\nYour task:\nAnalyze all of this information and generate a concise, actionable overview that prepares Cobi for the sales call. Focus on strategic value, not repetition of facts.\nOutput Structure:\n\n● Potential Fit with Shout About Us (2-3 sentences) – How our review data, \nresponses, or insights could create value for their platform or customers.\n● Call Focus Areas (3-5 bullet points) – What to emphasize during the call to \nmaximize alignment and close likelihood (e.g. speed to market, dev cost savings, \npartner examples, API simplicity, SDK plans, etc.).\n● Strategic Angle (1 paragraph) – Summarize the “storyline” that will likely \nresonate most with them (e.g., “Position SAU as the infrastructure layer for their \nvoice-of-customer or AI insights roadmap”).\n● Next Step Suggestion (optional) – The best call-to-action or follow-up offer to \nmove the deal forward (e.g. free trial, sample data, co-branded dashboard demo).\nBe direct, persuasive, and strategic — the goal is to equip Cobi to guide the conversation \ntoward a partnership or pilot.\n\n\nOutput Format : \n\n{\n\"potential_fit_with_shout_about_us\": \"___\",\n\"call_focus_areas\": \"___\",\n\"strategic_angle\": \"___\",\n\"next_step_suggestion\" :\"___\"\n}"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        3968,
        624
      ],
      "id": "4b32234b-c7a7-4899-b069-f59ed943e381",
      "name": "Shout About Us Help AI Agent",
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Based on the information below, please generate the pre-call planning document :\n\nMeeting Time : {{ $json.start_dateTime }} (Convert it to Readable Format)\n\nMeeting Title: {{ $('Set Details for Formatter Agent').item.json.metting_title }}\n\nAttendee : {{ $('Set Details for Formatter Agent').item.json.attendee_full_name }} \n\nAttendee Title : : {{ $('Set Details for Formatter Agent').item.json.attendee_title }}\n\nAttendee LinkedIn : {{ $('Set Details for Formatter Agent').item.json.attendee_linkedin_url }}\n\n\nCompany Description: {{ $('Set Details for Formatter Agent').item.json.company_description }}\n\nHow Shout About Us Can Help: \n\nPotential Fit with Shout About Us : {{ $json.potential_fit_with_shout_about_us }}\n\nCall Focus Areas : {{ $json.call_focus_areas }}\n\nStrategic Angle : {{ $json.strategic_angle }}\n\nNext Step Suggestion : {{ $json.next_step_suggestion }}\n\nSalesforce Interaction Summary : {{ $json.salesforce_interaction_summary }}\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=You are an expert Sales Strategist AI. Your purpose is to synthesize raw information about a prospect and create a concise, structured pre-call planning document in a simple JSON format.\n\nInstructions:\n\nRead all the provided information, which may include company details, contact information, and a summary of previous interactions from a CRM like Salesforce.\n\nAnalyze the content to generate a summary for each of the following strategic areas:\n\nmeeting_details: Identify and list the key attendees, their titles, and their roles in the meeting.\n\ncompany_overview: Write a brief, one-paragraph summary of what the prospect's company does.\n\nvalue_proposition: Summarize how our product/service can help this specific prospect and why it's a strong potential fit for their business.\n\ncall_strategy: Outline the most important topics to focus on and describe the overall strategic angle or approach for the call.\n\nnext_steps_suggestion: Propose a clear, actionable next step to suggest at the end of the conversation.\n\nsalesforce_summary: Condense the provided CRM data into a concise summary covering the relationship status, key insights, and primary action items.\n\nYour analysis must be objective and based only on the information provided.\n\nYour final output must be a single, valid JSON object that strictly follows the required structure. Do not add any text or explanations outside of the JSON object itself."
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        4704,
