    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Automated Workflow for Generating Personalized Meeting Summaries and Google Docs\n\n- **Step 1:** Trigger the workflow manually to start the process.\n- **Step 2:** Retrieve upcoming events from a specified Google Calendar.\n- **Step 3:** Filter out cancelled events and ignore emails from specific domains (e.g., shoutaboutus.com).\n- **Step 4:** Extract attendee email and derive the company domain from the email address.\n- **Step 5:** Enrich attendee information using Apollo API to get full name, LinkedIn URL, job title, and company name.\n- **Step 6:** Use an AI agent to generate a concise company description based on the company name and domain.\n- **Step 7:** Use a second AI agent to generate a personalized explanation of how Shout About Us can help the company, tailored to the company description, meeting details, and attendee title.\n- **Step 8:** Format all gathered information and AI-generated content into a structured Markdown summary suitable for Google Docs.\n- **Step 9:** Create a new Google Docs document with a dynamic title based on the company name.\n- **Step 10:** Update the Google Docs document by inserting the formatted meeting summary content.\n- **Step 11:** The workflow processes multiple events and attendees in batches, ensuring scalability and efficient handling of multiple meetings.\n",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 1120,
        "color": 4
      },
